code: @Override protected ListViewSerializer<T> createOuterSerializerWithNestedSerializers(TypeSerializer<?>[] nestedSerializers) {     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     TypeSerializer<List<T>> listSerializer = (TypeSerializer<List<T>>) nestedSerializers[0].     return new ListViewSerializer<>(listSerializer). }
@Override protected TypeSerializer<?>[] getNestedSerializers(ListViewSerializer<T> outerSerializer) {     return new TypeSerializer<?>[] { outerSerializer.getListSerializer() }. }
